ED_Title: Report  of the Economic and Social Council
ED_DecisionText: At its 38th plenary meeting, on 13 November 2025, the General Assembly took note of the report of the Economic and Social Council  (Footnote: Official Records of the General Assembly, Eightieth Session, Supplement No. 3 (A/80/3).).
ED_Disclaimer: The final text of this decision will be contained in document A/80/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
